#### Title Format Rules
- **Category Prefix**: Use appropriate category in brackets
- **Main Title**: Human-readable, SEO-optimized title
- **Subtitle**: Additional context or clarification
- **Length**: Keep total title under 70 characters

### Date Management Best Practices
- **Current Date**: Always use today's date obtained via command line
- **Date Consistency**: Ensure folder name date matches front matter date
- **Time Zone**: Use local timezone for date determination
- **Date Updates**: Update `lastmod` when content is significantly revised

### Automated Content Bundle Creation
```powershell
# Complete script for creating a new content bundle
$today = Get-Date -Format "yyyy-MM-dd"
$year = Get-Date -Format "yyyy"
$title = "your-seo-optimized-title-here"
$folderName = "$today-$title"

# For English word posts
$englishWord = "juvenile"  # Replace with actual word
